      '\n- Outline three sources which provide evidence for evolution.\t<span class="marks">[3]</span>\n\n- Describe how both bats and butterflies have wings.\t\t<span class="marks">[5]</span>\n\n- Explain the process of speciation with at least one named example. \t<span class="marks">[7]</span>\n\n',
